{"tid":1920853,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"新機唔知咩事 跑FurMark會死機....","createTime":"2020-03-11T17:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T04:14:52.000Z","uid":10230,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e2d7688a1f9d4f3f0ae8c12500bd09ed8598d8d3","tid":1920853,"uid":10230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T17:15:10.000Z","msg":"cpu i5 9400f 1120<br />\ngpu ausu rtx2060 super gaming 8gb 3650<br />\nausu b360-h gaming 850 <br />\n三星 860evo 500gb ssd  650<br />\nwd 1tb 300<br />\nkingston 8gb 2666mz ram x2  560<br />\nfsp raider 2 80plus sliver 750w   599<br />\ncooler master mb511 rgb 581<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係我部機 2月17買。。<br />\n<br />\n上星期打gta會花畫面之後死機。<br />\n去桌面<br />\n用FurMark 跑 二秒就花畫面之後黑<br />\n之後彈桌面。<br />\n<br />\n但較低畫面玩gta就無問題。<br />\n<br />\n我就試左以下幾樣野。<br />\n<br />\n用舊gpu  1050ti <br />\n跑FurMark 完全無事。<br />\n<br />\n拎2060s去代理試<br />\n佢跑FurMark 同其他幾個測gpu 程式都無事。<br />\n個代理話可能火牛 叫我甩hhd 試<br />\n會多左幾十w電  如跑FurMark 耐d先死 就係火牛事<br />\n<br />\n我反去就甩左hhd插反2060s<br />\n跑funmakr  呢次跑到一半先死。<br />\n<br />\n係咪好肯定係火牛事？<br />\n<br />\n但成750w  無理由唔夠力推 我條list...<br />\n<br />\n有冇可能係第2D野死?<br />\n如果係牛..<br />\n換個隻牛好定去代理換好...<br />\n定直接換火牛算..."},{"pid":"ef8a052d46b43a9e652125097cf0e71ea6909d58","tid":1920853,"uid":248695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T17:19:10.000Z","msg":"就咁睇牛出事嘅機會好大<br />\n<br />\n一係你問人借隻牛返嚟試<br />\n<br />\n一係做返啲基本嘢<br />\n甩ram reset cmos再裝返再行一次"},{"pid":"8aeecc81c796bf424167417231c3205e27225ea7","tid":1920853,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T17:32:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1572938e99a7869d92449c08674d3a6ba83ef6ac","tid":1920853,"uid":89514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T17:33:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e89e596a1254f4e8f69cc15cdb8887f67cee582","tid":1920853,"uid":10230,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T17:46:37.000Z","msg":"買過隻算.... 邊隻好"}